               <p>Before Mr. Justice Littledale.</p>
               <p>179. 
               
                  <persName id="t18301209-179-defend1592" type="defendantName">
                     WILLIAM 
                     KITCHEN
                  <interp inst="t18301209-179-defend1592" type="surname" value="KITCHEN"></interp>
